<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Password Changed Successfully</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { background-color: #f4f6f9; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #1a1a2e; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 16px; }
    .card { background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%); padding: 36px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header-logo { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #e94560; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
    .header-logo span { color: #ffffff; }
    .body { padding: 40px; }
    .success-icon { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .success-circle { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 72px; height: 72px; border-radius: 50%; background: #f0fff4; border: 3px solid #68d391; font-size: 32px; }
    .greeting { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a2e; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .text { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #4a5568; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .info-box { background: #f0fff4; border-left: 4px solid #38a169; border-radius: 6px; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 24px 0; }
    .info-box p { font-size: 14px; color: #276749; line-height: 1.6; }
    .divider { height: 1px; background: #e2e8f0; margin: 28px 0; }
    .warning { background: #fff5f5; border-left: 4px solid #e53e3e; border-radius: 6px; padding: 16px 20px; }
    .warning p { font-size: 13px; color: #742a2a; line-height: 1.6; }
    .timestamp { font-size: 12px; color: #a0aec0; margin-top: 20px; }
    .footer { background: #f7fafc; padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
    .footer-text { font-size: 12px; color: #a0aec0; line-height: 1.6; }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .body { padding: 28px 24px; }
      .footer { padding: 20px 24px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="header-logo">Electro<span>Pi</span> <span style="color:#a0aec0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;">PM</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="body">
        <div class="success-icon">
          <div class="success-circle">✓</div>
        </div>

        <p class="greeting">Hi {{name}},</p>
        <p class="text">Your password has been successfully changed. You can now log in to your <strong>ElectroPi PM</strong> account using your new password.</p>

        <div class="info-box">
          <p>✅ <strong>Account:</strong> {{email}}<br>
          ⏰ <strong>Changed at:</strong> {{changedAt}}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="divider"></div>

        <div class="warning">
          <p>⚠️ <strong>Didn't change your password?</strong><br>
          If you did not make this change, your account may have been compromised. Please contact support immediately and change your password as soon as possible.</p>
        </div>

        <p class="timestamp">This notification was sent to {{email}}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p class="footer-text">
          This email was sent by <strong>ElectroPi Project Management</strong><br>
          This is an automated security notification — please do not reply.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
